Rating: 4
Flan is a favorite here in Tampa and the pumpkin flan is a perfect holiday dessert!

Rating: 4
Absolutely delicious. The flavour combination of coconut and pumpkin is surprisingly fantastic! I've served this to guests twice and received rave reviews each time. The hardest part for me was finding a pan large enough for the hot water bath.